{"tid":397373,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得7-11 出過電視機","createTime":"2017-09-12T12:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T02:35:32.000Z","uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35a3e9c4c3f5fe9767d9e251b34226753293b867","tid":397373,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"突然醒起細個屋企有部灰色既野,好大舊<br />\n有個6,7吋左右既黑白電視MON<br />\n同埋有個電筒<br />\n好似叫super 7 唔知係咪711出既,有無人有印象?"},{"pid":"49ad902645d389bb7aa2ebdbce5aa417926694f8","tid":397373,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"係10幾年前嘅事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啤酒商為促銷啤酒，同便利店合作，推出戶外組合。<br />\n用鉛酸電池，著光管、收音機、迷你黑白模擬電視。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bff292ab19031dd2f24d35b0571795f7f382920","tid":397373,"uid":13818,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"曼德拉效應"},{"pid":"d6570d3f081309d20849bf31f67c660279fcf9ce","tid":397373,"uid":26506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曼德拉效應</blockquote><br />\n曼你老母德拉效應"},{"pid":"0b3f567943a8e8f2297782323af61579f3e3c06f","tid":397373,"uid":121885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係10幾年前嘅事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啤酒商為促銷啤酒，同便利店合作，推出戶外組合。<br />\n用鉛酸電池，著光管、收音機、迷你黑白模擬電視。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都記得有,電視賣廣告,果陣讀小學,好撚想要台野<br />\n<br />\n覺得有左可以無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4334ef999f1577354465458a5879e9438b45944","tid":397373,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:17:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80b934bcba08327a4ff8cad48e02ae05ca1d2862","tid":397373,"uid":133256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco